props.name: current
props.description: If `true`, indicates that the user is currently on this page. This takes precedence over `active`.

props.name: active
props.description: If `true`, indicates that the user is within this group of pages in the navigation hierarchy.

props.name: text
props.description: Text for the navigation item. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: href
props.description: URL of the navigation item anchor.

props.name: component
props.description: The component used to render the link, for example `RouterLink`. Will default to `a` if an `href` is provided or no link otherwise.

slots.name: default
slots.description: The content of the navigation item. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
